entries.s_b0ab3e88: Oh!  You had me going there.  Well you've earned that, anyway.

entries.s_ae21cb72: Thanks to you!  Great work, %NU.  You've really earned these credits.

entries.s_9928bf27: You're an odd one, %NU.  But you do deserve to be compensated for the risks you take.
entries.s_943f6352: Alright. Hurry up and come back when you're ready.
entries.s_9248b2ba: Well you've certainly earned it.  I'll talk to you later.

entries.s_8a84109d: It must be your lucky day. I actually do have some elective duty missions. Take a look and tell me what you want to do.

entries.s_7ac0f961: How do you do. Captain Kaydine, at your service.
entries.s_76e6f264: Captain %TU! You are doing a fantastic job! I think you've grown enough as a pilot to warrant advanced training. What area interests you most?

entries.s_6cd96c01: Of course! There's no end to the missions... and there's no time for me to do them. Your job will be to take my place on the RSF duty roster - in exchange for training, which I will personally administer. Sound like a good deal?
entries.s_6c6f3940: How do you do sir! Captain Kaydine, at your service.
entries.s_65042122: So, I hear you were not able to destroy all three of the Ay'Nat Legion's outlaw fighters. But don't worry - I'll get RSF record keepers to hold off marking this one a failure. You ready to try again?
entries.s_63053557: Good! What duty element do you want to participate in today?
entries.s_57ba8a73: In that case, let's get you back up there. This time make sure the RSF prison ship makes it out of the system. Good luck!
entries.s_4aa3066e: Ah yes! Good choice! Learning to fly many different types of ships makes an effective pilot!
entries.s_4a743aa7: The Ay'Nat pirate legion is mounting an aggressive campaign for control here in Naboo. They're building fast... so we need to strike at their leadership, and send them scrambling.

entries.s_387397fb: Did you hear how the RSF Guard foiled an attempt by Ay'Nat Legion pirates to detonate proton packs in the Palace reactor?
entries.s_35fb22d6: The Royal family has increased security in the wake of recent theft. A number of Her Majesty's personal freight ships have been hijacked in recent days. This is partly why you're here, I imagine... because we're hiring space pilots?
entries.s_326deced: No, I am in this for the money
entries.s_30297e22: Recover ships stolen by the Ay'Nat Legion.
entries.s_2fd7906f: Why do all you kids want to fly around looking like pirates? Ugh! But... I'll admit... you will need the handling capabilities of the Kihraxz Light Fighter if you're going to survive a pre-emptive strike against the Ay'Nat Legion's elite starfighter assassins! That's for sure.

entries.s_287eca83: We needed to get that prisoner ship out of the Naboo system to keep the Empire happy. You don't want the Empire to be angry with us, do you?
entries.s_2847218: Being a war-hero, my life is rather complex. I perform a long list of Palace functions... almost none of which involve starflight. For those matters, I need able-bodied pilots such as yourself.
